name: Le petit Rahan / Les voleurs d'histoires

name: Prion

description:
This issue consists of a hand painted figurine and a magazine on the issues featured character, Superman.

The Forever Evil set ends with issue 96, White King - Superman. (Action Comics)
name: Superman

description: Paris, 1793. Marie Crossholz manages the wax museum set up by her father. In exchange for bribes, some executioners allow her to mould the faces of guillotined aristocrats... After the French Revolution, Marie Crossholz becomes Mrs Tussaud. Disappointed by the marriage, she leaves for London with the ambition to create a wax museum there. New fights and other tumultuous adventures await her... Thirty years later, in 1835, she inaugurates the famous Tussaud Museum of Baker Street in London, which today continues to grow with new celebrities and attracts millions of visitors!

The pupil Ducoboo is nice and a joker, but also a notorious dunce—a “quality” that is no bed of roses…One must be awfully resourceful to avoid the humiliating dunce’s cap! But Ducoboo is brimming with imagination…. Through gags, some stranger than others, this series champions values such as friendship and the right to be different, and tackles subjects such as boy-girl and parent-child relationships.
name: King of the Dunces

description: It’s not by counting the flies on the ceiling that one becomes a star in maths... And one must be really resourceful to avoid the beckoning finger of the teacher and the humiliation of the dunce cap! And Leonie, who still detests copiers... So, Ducoboo invents the answers that he can’t steal from his neighbour. He has cause to regret doing so because, although very fertile, his imagination plays tricks on him and he often ends up “In the Corner”!
name: In the Corner!

description: What would a class be without a dunce? A bit like a curry without spice. And Ducoboo sure spices up his fellow pupils' days. Not one lesson goes by without flavour--with him, school is an endless string of break-times. Of course, there’s always Leonie, the terribly gifted girl who doesn't put up with Ducoboo's messing and doesn't believe in sharing knowledge. Of course, there’s also the teacher, whose index finger turns out to be more threatening than ever… No, school life isn’t one long, smooth ride: For some, the school year is perhaps the most dangerous time of all!
name: Your Answers or Your Life!

description: Ducoboo’s life isn’t easy. Being the king of dunces–while still managing to avoid wearing the “crown” too often–takes work, dedication, and an awful lot of imagination. It also takes a proper target: Leonie, the gifted girl who doesn’t like to share her answers with His Majesty. It’s a constant war of wits between these two, under the disbelieving eye of the long-suffering teacher, fought with wigs, cameras and magical pencil-sharpeners. And when school’s over, the beach is the new battlefield!
name: The Class Struggle

description:
Jean-Baptiste Poulain has been hired by the Baron of Brac to tutor his son. When the young teacher arrives on the island off the coast of Brittany, he’s immediately struck by how much the population seems to both hate and fear their lord. Which doesn’t stop the locals from going after the aristocrat’s people. Jean-Baptiste is brutally attacked – just after Nolwenn, the baron’s son, is found beaten to death…

Note: The digital edition (3/20/2015) for this volume was released before the print edition.
name: The Isle of Brac

description:
Jean-Baptiste Poulain comes to Auvergne in central France to investigate the deaths of two young women. Both were killed one year apart in the same barbaric, ritual way, their bodies left near the Black Virgin Chapel ... and the day approaches when another victim could turn up. Unfortunately, he’s going to have to struggle against the locals’ superstitions, the hostility of the authorities, and the hatred all seem to direct at the neighbouring gypsies.

Note: The digital edition (3/20/2015) for this volume was released before the print edition.
name: The Black Virgin

description: The forces of the 3rd Reich surge into France. The Panzer Division’s speed takes the Allies by surprise, and French forces are soon defeated, while the British Expeditionary force is blocked off in the “Dunkirk Pocket,” from which they barely escape. In the face of a victorious Reich, the fate of the world will rest for a few months on the shoulders of a handful of men: the RAF pilots.
name: Battle of Britain

description:
It's the ultimate battle of good vs. evil in this series finale!

Will Devah and Decoda prove strong enough to defeat Archangel Michael and Syntax and the armies of Heaven and Hell?

Julien D’Arcy, the oldest and most dangerous of Demian's enemies, is back. And while our chevalier is hunting him again, many things are about to change. The beautiful Dalila is spinning her web to rebuild the Trait D’Union. Viviane is fighting the terrible illness that caught her. Marie is more and more tempted to go back to her old job in the police force. And Gaston? He's on the verge of taking a very, very dangerous decision...
name: Debito di sangue

description: Accoding to the tradition of the Pennsylvanian Amish, the youngsters, after their coming of age, go out of their community, travelling to see the outside world. Only then they can choose if they want back in the realm of their religion, with its strict rules, or if they will become non-believers. It's a time called “Rumspringa”, that the young Amish boys and girls can use to experiment with the freedom to drink, smoke and do the usual things of the kids their age. When, in Philadelphia, during their “Rumspringa”, some young Amish go so far as to kill other people, the Law springs to action — a young Amish "renegade" who's now working for the United States police. He will be joined by Harlan and Kurjak, because two of those killers have a peculiar feature: they're vampires! Their Master of the Night is waiting for them in a village suspended in the space-time, New Helder, where the community rules are very different from the usual... and far more creepy!
name: Orrore tra gli Amish

description: A magic message written in runes summons Harlan Draka and his old Icelandic double, Egil-one-hand to Iceland. In the past, Egil and the blond witch Gudrun helped young wizard Galdra Loftur to steal the tenebrous grimoire Raudskinna, the “book of red skin”! Now, following the tracks of the kidnappers of the bishop of Reykjavik, who left a whiff of brimstone behind themselves, Harlan and Gudrun Finngadottir travel to the interior of Iceland, where there was one of the entrances to the mysterious University of Hell. It is there, in the abyss of the Black School, that, along with an unfortunate Icelandic cop, they will have to reluctantly enroll for the infernal courses of the Other Side and follow the bloody classes of its demonic teachers...
name: Gli studenti della scuola nera

description: The nightmare is back. The alien Morb visited the Eart again. In the countryside of New Jersey, a flying saucer crashed on a farm. Its occupants disappeared and Brad Barron is called to be a part of the search group, along with a team of soldiers. It will be a hunt where the prey and hunter roles continuously reverse. Meanwhile, inside Brad's mind, a lost memory is resurfacing, shedding a new, disquieting light on his past.
name: Terrore dal cielo

description: After the problems in her relationship with Branko, May goes to the Silent Heaven satellite to investigate on a murder case. Once on the huge and idyllic orbiting station, the beautiful Alfa agent finds out that a mysterious killer, once believed to be dead, could be alive; and he could be the root of her personal distress...
name: Quando la ragione tace

description: In a distant future, the telepath sisterhood faces a terrible and dark enemy. Hordes of terrifying monsters appear out of thin air, destroying the last human resistance — only a woman endowed with extraordinary powers, who comes from a faraway time, will be able to piece together her past and find the origin of the menace, discovering the way to free the Earth!
name: La guerra del buio

description:
This issues contains 5 stories:

Triplice attacco

Erika, Tanya and Monique, the three Walkirye, are involved in a desperate mission that takes them to go into action at the same time underground, in air and at sea, to prevent a terrifying disaster that could provoke the death of hundreds of innocent people!

Uomini e superuomini

An investigation to find the identity of a pair of acrobatic thieves puts a strain to the relationship between May and Branko once again...

La tata

Betty and Sigmund’s marriage is undergoing a crisis, due to the fact that they seem unable to have children. But the unexpected involvement in the kidnapping of a young boy forces the woman to face her contradictory feelings...

Il dubbio

Link the android must try to frame a trader of pirated technology, but things will get more intricated then he thought...

Le due guerriere

Sent to the Territory on a mission, Legs and Tanya are caught in a dangerous illegal fight between giant mobile armor suits.
name: Triplice attacco

description:
A double mission for the Argo squad!

The crew of Asteroide Argo is sent to follow an important scientific panel, where a new and revolutionary technology will be revealed— something that could change the future of our galaxy forever. When a puzzling murder happen, Major Helen Sheldon will have to employ all her resources to find the killer, while robot McCloud, in a mission on planet Comby, will be face to face with the mighty Ptikerix!
name: Intrigo su Jhang 2

description:
An unexpected secret under the surface of ZE90!...

A Kundingas scientific expedition vanishes while exploring a faraway planet. The members of the Asteroide Argo crew are sent on a rescue mission, but there they’ll find a hidden, unexpected threat that could change the political balance of the Other Galaxy!
name: Zona esterna
